<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<div style="font-size: 12pt;">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br><b><br>Your business insurance policy is due for renewal.</b></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><ul><li><b>Policy number:</b>&nbsp;<i>[policy number]</i></li><li><b>Expiry date</b>:&nbsp;<i>[expiry date]</i></li></ul></div><div><div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">If you wish to renew your business insurance policy, please contact us on&nbsp;<b>01242 808740</b>&nbsp;between the hours&nbsp;<b>8:00am – 5:30pm Monday-Friday</b>&nbsp;and our team will complete your purchase over the phone.<br><br><b>Don't want to renew your policy?</b></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Let us know by either email or phone and we will update our records.</font><br><br><font face="Arial, sans-serif">We hope you find our policy suits all your business needs and we look forward to hearing from you.</font><br><span style="background-color: white;"><br><font face="arial"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Kind regards,</font><br></span></font></span><span style="background-color: white; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><br></font><font face="Arial, sans-serif">{!User.FirstName}<br></font></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: white; font-size: 12pt;">Customer Service Team<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: white; font-size: 12pt;"><br>E:&nbsp;</span><a href="mailto:customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk" style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: white; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk</a><br><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: white; font-size: 12pt;">T: 01242 808 740</span></div></div>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>